Author: flortotheno
Text: When I started counting I measured a 200ml portion of milk and then put it on a ceramic mug. I made a mark w a marker so I just pour it into the mug instead of a measuring cup. Same w cereal, and I was gifted a coffee cup that measures exactly a cup by my best friend. Best gift ever.
